【Topic】Lab for Cell Dynamics at the Institute of Molecular Biology at Academia Sinica is recruiting research assistants and postdoctoral fellows

【職務名稱】博士後研究員/學、碩士級助理  (歡迎研發替代役)

【Job Title】Research Assistants/Postdoc Research Fellows

【實驗室網頁】
http://celldynamicslabchinese.strikingly.com/

【Lab Website】
http://celldynamicslab.strikingly.com/

【研究主題】
1)	單細胞系統生物學 。
2)	癌症代謝與表觀遺傳調節。
3)	癌症複合式 療法 。
4)	蛋白質體與代謝體學。

【Research Topics】
1)	Single-cell systems biology. 
2)	Cancer metabolism and epigenetic regulation。
3)	Rational design of cancer combinatorial therapies。
4)	Proteomics and metabolomics. 

【徵求條件】
生科或理工程背景。對量化、系統與合成生物學有興趣。我們尤其歡迎喜歡挑戰、有創意、想要學習跨領域研究的科學家。

【Qualification 】
We are particularly interested in recruiting open-minded and creative scientists interested in quantitative, systems and synthetic biology to join our team. You can be: 
1. Biologists with interests in cell biology, and have affinity to theory and computation.
2. Physicists/Bioinformaticians/Engineers with interests in genomics, dynamic systems, or statistical modeling, and passion to work on system-level biological questions.

